  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, combine the flour, salt, and cumin.",
    "Gradually add the water and mix until a dough forms.",
    "Knead the dough for 5 minutes and let it rest for 30 minutes.",
    "Divide the dough into 8 equal pieces.",
    "Roll out each piece into a thin circle.",
    "Spoon a tablespoon of duck confit onto one half of the circle.",
    "Sprinkle shredded cheese, chopped onion, and garlic on top.",
    "Fold the other half of the circle over to form a half-moon shape.",
    "Press the edges together to seal the empanada.",
    "Heat the vegan shortening in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the empanadas to the skillet, seam-side down, and cook for 3-4 minutes on each side.",
    "Serve hot with a side of smoked paprika, if desired."
  ],
